\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li567\ri567 Instead of using the standard puzzle, the user may enter the name of a file containing a puzzle. Four text files containing different 5\'d75 grid puzzles have been provided: puzzle1, puzzle2, puzzle3 and puzzle4.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li567\ri567 There are errors in the implementation of the puzzle in the Skeleton Program, which means that it does not work in the way described in this Preliminary Material under all circumstances.\par
